query_templated.1806:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?image WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:painting] .
?item wdt:[property:depicts]/wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity] wd:[entity:Haarlem] .
?item wdt:[property:image] ?image .
BIND(MD5(CONCAT(str(?item),str(RAND()))) as ?random)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en"}
} ORDER BY ?random
LIMIT 100

PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?idiom ?idiomLabel ?lemma ?lemmaLabel
WHERE {
?idiom wdt:P31 wd:Q184511 .
?idiom wdt:P407 wd:Q9035 .
?idiom wdt:P6404 ?lemma .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY ?idiomLabel
LIMIT 10
